==English==
===Noun===
'''waterman''' (plural '''[[watermen]]''')
[[Category:English nouns]]
[[Category:English irregular plurals]]
# A [[man]] skilled in multiple [[acquatic]] disciplines, such as [[surfing]], [[bodysurfing]], undersea [[diving]], [[canoe]] paddling, [[fishing]], etc.
===Usage notes===
Describing someone as a ''waterman'' is the highest [[honour]] in the surfing [[community]] and is [[reserved]] to those with long-standing and indisputably significant all-round [[achievement]]s.
